# --- MovieLens data (NOT redistributable — download separately) ---
# GroupLens does not permit redistribution of the dataset, so the raw files are
# kept out of the repo. See data/raw/README.md for how to fetch them.
# The Streamlit app does NOT need these (it loads results/artifacts.joblib).
data/raw/*.csv
data/raw/*.zip
data/raw/ml-latest-small/
data/processed/*

# Keep folder placeholders / instructions
!data/raw/README.md
!data/processed/README.md

# NOTE: results/ IS committed on purpose — results/artifacts.joblib (~8 MB),
# results/figures/*.png and results/metrics.csv are required by the deployed app.
